span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港憲法保衛戰</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地名正言順出師有名係為咗保衛香港憲法給予香港人既自由、文化、以及一切香港根基，兩個月前已經提出<br />\n<br />\n[名不正則言不順] 陳雲：這次是香港憲法保衛戰，不是什麼「反送中」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1207678\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1207678</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b70baa11978066a04cf381fad14dce8ad948588b","tid":1513228,"uid":137344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:55:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3d47235bd04c21cec7f1fd93f0588743abb02670","tid":1513228,"uid":137344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:55:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"72d80fc10302b1dd33cfcc21617d46bb3bad251d","tid":1513228,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:55:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">真普選運動</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z9BB58b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz9BB58b.gif&h=5f59beb8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b202d6b0548748d8bc7c35564c90fdf06c2e30cb","tid":1513228,"uid":291805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T08:57:27.000Z","msg":"借位唔好意思:<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Rh9GGd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Rh9GGd.jpg&h=fc50af02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌網頁:</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%e5%91%bd%e9%81%8b%e8%87%aa%e9%81%b8%e9%81%99%e6%8e%a7%e5%99%a8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25e5%2591%25bd%25e9%2581%258b%25e8%2587%25aa%25e9%2581%25b8%25e9%2581%2599%25e6%258e%25a7%25e5%2599%25a8%2F&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5A0QAWntaMGUWBfwPSaCbl8%3D&h=a54bc8e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%e5%91%bd%e9%81%8b%e8%87%aa%e9%81%b8%e9%81%99%e6%8e%a7%e5%99%a8/</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">原post: </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1513167/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1513167/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q3ryoUC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ3ryoUC.jpg&h=a72cf205&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTVB報導偏頗，不盡不實，屢次抹黑反送中示威活動，出賣香港市民。<br />\n在此呼籲全港18區抗爭者，合力將所有酒樓，茶餐廳，醫院，護老院，健身室等公共空間的電視轉台。<br />\n<br />\n由TVB 81/82/83/84/85 轉去 港台 31/32，開電視 77 或 Viu TV 99台。<br />\n<br />\n小弟對萬用遙控略有認識，在過去一個月，與工廠開發了一款<span style=\"color: red;\">抗爭專用遙控器</span> (universal remote)。<br />\n<br />\n產品可控制9大電視品牌 + 1個自選品牌，於出廠時已預設轉台及其他基本功能。 簡易操作如下：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 查看電視品牌<br />\n<br />\n2. 按鍵選擇該品牌<br />\n<br />\n3. 按CH+-鍵轉台<br />\n<br />\n現眾籌HKD120000，當中已包括開發和測試費用，4000件大貨，4%眾籌平台手續費，運輸到全港18區和18區智能櫃費用。</span><br />\n<br />\n如眾籌達標，將隨即下訂單，預計約30天內交貨。<br />\n<br />\n請捐款者screen cap捐款成功畫面，email到freehkremote@gmail.com，告知希望取貨的地區。<br />\n<br />\n當貨到香港，我將以捐款者的email聯絡，告知所屬地區的取貨密碼和地址。<br />\n<br />\n這次眾籌屬個人自發，沒有人手，故只能用honour system，煩請捐$50者自取一件，$100者自取兩件，如此類推。 由於智能櫃有時間限制，請於通知發出後40小時內取貨。 由於無法控制參與者是否全部自律，恕不能保證捐款者一定能取得產品，只能做到盡量安排，先到先得。<br />\n<br />\n眾籌目的，不像Kickstarter或Indiegogo買產品，而是要令更多的香港抗爭者加入全港轉台行列。<br />\n<br />\n多謝支持！！ 香港人加油！！"},{"pid":"0c3a83c94eed169f1ef7f5910ccbdd6535f9b153","tid":1513228,"uid":137344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:01:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"33574880f704c5a990d75587003b2bce07c26931","tid":1513228,"uid":137344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:01:42.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"82df7814047af695ffcd25a59d90145f045e11e4","tid":1513228,"uid":67424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:02:22.000Z","msg":"洋紫荊革命"},{"pid":"ca5226cdf766093fb80327819e308f61cfc69cc4","tid":1513228,"uid":63311,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:02:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\